title: Grateful Dead Live at St. Paul Civic Center on 1983-06-25
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC 24/96; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Wave > Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Cassidy, West L.A. Fadeaway, My Brother Esau, Big Railroad Blues, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Might As Well

Set 2

Touch Of Gray-> Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Women Are Smarter, Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Throwing Stones-> Black Peter-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> One More Saturday Night, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

reviews.review_text:
This is a fine show There are others from the same period that get tons of love. This one is likely as good as any of them. Poor unloved show.

Particularly like UJB, Baby Blue, Black Peter, Ship of Fools.
